snippet.title: GoatRunnerReleaseV2
snippet.description:
Link to play store (Android)
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.bitflexer.goatrunner

Goat Runner is a difficult platform runner game. Available for Android and soon for iOS (Mobile & Desktop).

Get a great indie platformer for free:


Second release includes
* Added coins
* Added level selection screen
* Save coins and time
